{"tid":2161465,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美售台66架F-16V戰機  料斥620億 配頂級雷達注視即攻擊","createTime":"2020-08-17T14:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T14:35:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f104c4066ccbd786a5bd99ae788db0a91e1849c7","tid":2161465,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:25:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200816/S4VBIGSOBFDVZNT4XZYF5ZLEKM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200816%2FS4VBIGSOBFDVZNT4XZYF5ZLEKM%2F&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21KZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=8a3dc986\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200816%2FS4VBIGSOBFDVZNT4XZYF5ZLEKM%2F&h=092ee6b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200816/S4VBIGSOBFDVZNT4XZYF5ZLEKM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美售台66架F-16V戰機 <br />\n料斥620億 配頂級雷達注視即攻擊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_c-PSjzmw63_K3ovA0NdXgOOyss=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R6FLMJCCVBABLGSA46EVMBPUCQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_c-PSjzmw63_K3ovA0NdXgOOyss%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR6FLMJCCVBABLGSA46EVMBPUCQ.jpg&h=60a60c86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■F-16V戰機擁有不少美國頂尖技術。<br />\n<br />\n台海關係緊張之際，根據彭博社等媒體報道，美國武器製造商洛歇馬田（Lockheed Martin）獲得10年總價共620億美元（下同．約4,805億港元）的F-16V定單，其中66架的買家正是台灣，外界估計台灣將動用80億（620億港元）購買戰機。今次是1992年後，台再次獲得美國的先進戰機。北京暫未回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美航母南海軍演 台模擬解放軍突襲<br />\n<br />\n根據美國國防部在美國時間14日上載的合約，洛歇馬田公司獲得為期10年、價值620億美元的合約，將。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n合約金額超美出口上限<br />\n<br />\n美國官方沒有公佈首輪買家身份，但美媒彭博社引述消息，今次合約總金額超過美國10年來，准許外國買家容許購買的上限。報道。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n彭博分析指，今次是自1992年美國老布殊宣佈出售150架F-16S戰機後，台灣再次獲。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n模擬戰力壓中國殲10<br />\n<br />\nF-16V是美國現時最常用的戰機，外界普遍相信比同屬第四代戰機的中國殲10C強大。F16V最大特色是裝有頂級的電子雷達「APG-83」，能同時追蹤20個目標，並且攻擊其中六個。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/X7jBQLxDm2358gkMm4CLpjMAF7M=/640x460/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7JA34QXYJ5BHJHPNLNIEB32MWU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FX7jBQLxDm2358gkMm4CLpjMAF7M%3D%2F640x460%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7JA34QXYJ5BHJHPNLNIEB32MWU.jpg&h=9ecc3f67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台灣將增購66架最新款的F-16V戰機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uRroPgGKIf3aHV42pGyTpR-ph30=/640x900/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5PTDMZ7MNNA4JIR5XSXOB6MZ4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuRroPgGKIf3aHV42pGyTpR-ph30%3D%2F640x900%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5PTDMZ7MNNA4JIR5XSXOB6MZ4Q.jpg&h=baf2fcf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e855890647be41fbe08b49ab65c9e73abc7f801","tid":2161465,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"泊翻幾十架戰機響台灣維修<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3647869113ff2255ab41ba9984d1e60b3718384e","tid":2161465,"uid":175930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:35:22.000Z","msg":"其實支支都想台仔買<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為夠近多諜易啲偷技術"}]}